title: Ep. #63 | BLACKPINK x Lady Gaga, 정국, Stray Kids
description:
Welcome back Daebak fam! Join Eric and Diane as they review 'Sour Candy' by Lady Gaga & BLACKPINK, 'Still With You' by Jungkook, and 'God's Menu' by Stray Kids. Eric also shares his 2 week quarantine experience in Korea and begs for a BLACKPINK comeback (little did he know... they're finally back)!


Make sure to subscribe to @daebakshow (IT’S FREE) and leave a comment, rating and/or review on Spotify, Apple Podcasts, Soundcloud, and YouTube.


Episodes are presented by @thedivestudios


Connect with us on all social media platforms @daebakshow and at http://www.divestudios.io/daebakshow !
